 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833944" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270.jpg" alt="碧昂斯在2025年格莱美奖上。学分：Sonja Flemming/CBS通过Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beyonce-grammys-2025@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833944" class="wp-caption-text">碧昂斯在2025年格莱美奖上。学分：Sonja Flemming/CBS通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>阿罗约随后表示，碧昂斯的奖项成功是因为“每个人都在每种类型中投票”，而“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>的Cat Sitter都会为最好的雷鬼和最佳乡村专辑投票”。</p><p>戈德伯格在美国白天的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WZtVELhvzU" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>演出</i></a>时说：“先生，您知道自己必须在音乐界成为格莱美选民吗？因此，猫保姆不能只投票。”</p><p>关于碧昂斯（Beyoncé）的胜利数量与其他音乐传奇人物相比，她说：“您知道格莱美奖（Grammys）于1959年开始时，只有28个类别，现在有94个类别？</p><p> “尽管弗兰克·辛纳屈（Frank Sinatra）获得了两张第一张专辑，但弗兰克·辛纳屈（Frank Sinatra）获得了六张提名的那一年，那天晚上，他只赢得了一张格莱美奖（Grammy）的专辑《封面》（Gromy），即使他的唱歌也不是为了唱歌。听着，伙计。你不能那样做。她赢得了。”</p><p>戈德堡继续说：“您想像白人一样坚持乡村音乐，也没有购买她的乡村专辑。来吧，伙计！人们投票支持它。有时您会获胜，有时您没有。与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>相同。坐下！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="福克斯新闻嘉宾对碧昂斯·格莱美（BeyoncéGrammy）赢得生气|视图" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9WZtVELhvzU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>碧昂斯（Beyoncé）参加了11项提名，参加了周日（2月2日）的仪式。这使她的总点向达到了99，这使她成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-is-now-officially-the-most-nominated-artist-in-grammy-history-3811696">格莱美历史上最受提名的艺术家</a>。她还保留了最格莱美奖的纪录，现在以35杆的成绩保持了纪录。</p><p>她的胜利也使历史悠久，因为她是第一个赢得最佳乡村专辑奖的黑人女性 - 尽管提名了很多，但这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-beyonce-finally-wins-album-of-the-year-3833943">标志性艺术家第一次赢得了年度专辑</a>。</p><p>最佳乡村专辑提名人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kacey-musgraves">Kacey Musgraves</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-viral-reaction-beyonce-beating-her-best-country-win-grammys-3834057">在颁奖典礼后因对碧昂丝的胜利而流行了</a>，一些歌迷认为Musgraves似乎并没有印象深刻地被她殴打。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-team-shoot-down-shade-claims-after-viral-beyonce-grammys-reaction-clip-3834440">Musgraves的团队昨天（2月4日）发表了一份声明</a>，击落了索赔。 </p><figure id="attachment_3603600" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603600" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603600" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="碧昂丝的“牛仔卡特”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (ma